# App Flow
## ASYCUDA Write-Off Manifest Portal
**Version:** 1.0.0

---

## Overview

The application flow is divided into 4 phases:
1. **Entry & System Validation** — User input, ASYCUDA checks, 6 pre-validation errors
2. **BL Validation** — Tradian, E-Customs, E-Valuator cross-check
3. **Amendment Workflow** — Digital MCS-117, admin review, rejection/re-submit loop
4. **Payment & Finalization** — Fine calculation, FF account charge, certificate generation

---

## Phase 1 — Entry & System Validation

```
User opens portal
        │
        ▼
[S1] Enter R-Number + Select Port
        │
        ▼
[S2] API: POST /asycuda/validate
     ├── Is ASYCUDA reachable?
     │       NO  → [E1] System down — retry
     │
     ├── Does R-Number exist for port + year?
     │       NO  → [E2] R-Number not found — check number
     │
     ├── Is form status = "assessed"?
     │       NO  → [E3] Not yet assessed — wait + refresh
     │
     ├── Is form locked by an officer?
     │       YES → [E4] Form locked — wait + refresh
     │
     ├── Does FF payment account have sufficient funds?
     │       NO  → [E5] Insufficient funds — top up
     │
     └── Is FF account code compatible with consignee code?
             NO  → [E6] Account mismatch — contact customs finance
```

---

## Phase 2 — BL Validation

```
All Phase 1 checks pass
        │
        ▼
Extract BL Number from ASYCUDA form data
        │
        ▼
API: GET /tradian/bl/{bl_number}
     ├── BL not found in Tradian?
     │       YES → [S3] BL Not Found
     │              ├── User contacts Tradian directly
     │              └── User submits BL Cancel Request [S12] → Phase 3 (admin review)
     │
        ▼
API: GET /ecustoms/verify/{bl_number}
     ├── BL not registered in E-Customs?
     │       YES → [S6] Technical Error — contact IT
     │
        ▼
API: POST /evaluator/validate
     Body: { bl_number, gross_weight, package_code, packs_number,
             exporter, consignee, carrier }
     │
     ├── All 7 fields match?
     │       YES → [S5] Write-Off Success ✓ TERMINAL
     │
     └── 1+ fields mismatch?
             YES → [S4] Field Mismatch — shows comparison table
                    └── User clicks "Apply for Amendment" → Phase 3
```

