## Phase 3 — Amendment Workflow

```
Entry points:
  [S4] Field mismatch → amendment
  [S4] Late manifest link → late manifest amendment
  [S3] BL cancel request [S12]
        │
        ▼
[S7] Digital MCS-117 Amendment Form
     │   - Pre-fills manifest details from ASYCUDA data
     │   - Pre-checks failing fields from S4
     │   - Auto-calculates fine:
     │       Late manifest:  MVR 3,000
     │       Tier I fields:  MVR 500
     │       Tier II fields: MVR 1,000 (higher tier wins)
     │   - User fills: content after change, reason, declaration
     │   - User uploads: required documents (1–4 depending on type)
     │
        ▼
API: POST /amendment/submit
     Returns: { amendment_ref, submitted_at, status: "pending_review" }
        │
        ▼
[S8] Pending Review — status polling
     API: GET /amendment/status/{amendment_ref}
     Polls every 60 seconds or on manual refresh
        │
        ├── status = "rejected"
        │       → [S9] Rejection screen (shows officer reason)
        │              └── "Re-submit" → [S7] (pre-filled, same ref)
        │
        └── status = "approved"
                → [S10] Payment Gateway → Phase 4
```

---

## Phase 4 — Payment & Finalization

```
[S10] Payment Gateway
      │   - Shows amendment summary
      │   - Shows fine breakdown + total
      │   - Charges to FF-[XXXXX] account
      │   - Payment method selection
      │
         ▼
API: POST /payment/initiate
     Body: { amendment_ref, ff_account, method, amount }
     Returns: { payment_ref, status }
        │
        ▼
API: POST /payment/confirm
     Body: { payment_ref, transaction_ref }
        │
        ▼
API: POST /writeoff/finalize
     Body: { amendment_ref, payment_ref }
     Returns: { writeoff_ref, finalized_at, certificate_url }
        │
        ▼
[S11] Write-Off Finalized ✓ TERMINAL
      - Download certificate available
      - Amendment record downloadable
```

