## API Dependency Map

```
S2 (Validate)
 ├── ASYCUDA     → /asycuda/manifest/{port}/{r_number}
 ├── ASYCUDA     → /asycuda/account/validate/{ff_code}/{consignee_code}
 ├── Tradian     → /tradian/bl/{bl_number}
 ├── E-Customs   → /ecustoms/verify/{bl_number}
 └── E-Valuator  → /evaluator/validate (POST, 7 fields)

S7 (Amendment Submit)
 └── Internal    → /amendment/submit (POST)

S8 (Status Poll)
 └── Internal    → /amendment/status/{ref} (GET)

S10 (Payment)
 ├── Internal    → /payment/initiate (POST)
 └── Internal    → /payment/confirm (POST)

S11 (Finalize)
 └── Internal    → /writeoff/finalize (POST)
```

