## State Machine

```
State:          idle
On submit S1:   loading

State:          loading
On E1:          asycuda_down
On E2:          r_not_found
On E3:          not_assessed
On E4:          form_locked
On E5:          insufficient_funds
On E6:          account_mismatch
On BL !tradian: bl_not_found
On BL !ecustom: ecustoms_error
On fields pass: write_off_success
On fields fail: field_mismatch

State:          field_mismatch
On amend:       amendment_form

State:          bl_not_found
On cancel req:  amendment_form (BL cancel mode)

State:          amendment_form
On submit:      pending_review

State:          pending_review
On reject:      rejected
On approve:     payment_ready

State:          rejected
On resubmit:    amendment_form

State:          payment_ready
On pay:         finalizing

State:          finalizing
On confirm:     finalized

Terminal states: write_off_success | finalized | asycuda_down (retry) | r_not_found | ecustoms_error
```

