## Error Recovery Map

| Error | Recovery Path | Who Acts |
|---|---|---|
| E1 ASYCUDA down | Retry after delay | System auto-retry or user manual |
| E2 R-No not found | Re-enter R-Number → S1 | User |
| E3 Not assessed | Wait + refresh | User (waits for officer) |
| E4 Form locked | Wait + refresh | User (waits for officer) |
| E5 Insufficient funds | Top up → retry | User (with finance) |
| E6 Account mismatch | Contact customs → S1 | User (with customs) |
| S3 BL not found | Contact Tradian OR submit cancel | User |
| S4 Field mismatch | Submit amendment → S7 | User |
| S6 E-Customs error | Contact IT | IT Department |
| S9 Rejected | Correct + re-submit → S7 | User |

